title: Multipart reader fails to return new Part
body:
by **staura**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Do a basic multipart upload
2. Successfully get the multipart reader 
3. Try to get the NextPart() from the multipart reader

What is the expected output?
*Part

What do you see instead?
unexpected EOF

Which compiler are you using (5g, 6g, 8g, gccgo)?
8g

Which operating system are you using?
i686 GNU/Linux - 2.6.36-2.dmz.5-liquorix-686

Which revision are you using?  (hg identify)
2f0fa51fa2da weekly/weekly.2011-04-27



Please provide any additional information below.
